dual audio remux of Nadia - Secret of Blue Water that I made because no one has made a proper one from the BD with styled subs, a Signs &amp; Songs track and the English audio all together.

The video and Japanese audio source is the Rising-Sun JP-BD 1080p FLAC release while the English AC3 audio comes from the DHD US-BD release (I've also included the unstyled PGS subs that come with this as well). I have both a styled Signs &amp; Songs only track and full styled subs track that I made from the Rising-Sun release (with the latest fixes).

The only weird thing was that for episodes 20 and 21, the US BD release skipped the recap after the OP for some reason so I used audio from a4e's DVD encode for those two (the volume may be a bit louder as well). If you know how to fix this, let me know.

I've checked all the episodes for the most part but if I missed anything, give me a shout out. I also included the Rising-Sun full subs and Signs &amp; Songs only subs that I made and used. I'll probably upload MEGA links to Kametsu in the future. And as always, please SEED.

Video: 1440x1080 8-bit (Rising-Sun JP-BD)
JP Audio: 2.0 16-bit FLAC (Rising-Sun JP-BD)
EN Audio: 2.0 AC3 (DHD US-BD) except for episodes 20 &amp; 21 (a4e US-DVD)
Signs &amp; Songs; Full English Subs: Rising-Sun (and deanzel edit)
